By":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:27:39.000Z","msg":"你個腦諗既野既解釋權係個官到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/nope.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66e4dd74c95da7358b64bae6de87dffe16862cb9","tid":2514382,"uid":56115,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"考慮各項因素後，嚴官以12個月監禁為量刑起點，因被告認罪而減刑至8個月。嚴官明言，本案涉及重大公眾利益，故即使考慮了被告的背景因素及<span class=\"red\">沒有案底，亦不構成減刑因素</span>。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&d=xOzWlad5M6duuHBPObmdOGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=a49508d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210503%2FAO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA%2F&h=fd68db83\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210503/AO6F4TXOENBGPLX3YELOT3C2UA/</a>"},{"pid":"27e6ba6335f013b639d54410679a13032529a41e","tid":2514382,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:50:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a33bbe32f7227bf8c413f01cd8a11cc65ab6074","tid":2514382,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:51:02.000Z","msg":"支那狗西"},{"pid":"b07c19e5448cf95b8ad888031558e813d6ec7db5","tid":2514382,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:00:29.000Z","msg":"嚴西<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b09ca53ffab1091667ff2bdfdccadabf21e87695","tid":2514382,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:32:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45de91b4c26594ac399f4eed75906276743b7443","tid":2514382,"uid":110043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:34:22.000Z","msg":"我發覺le d laser pointer 案<br />\n認罪就12個月減3份1<br />\n唔認打輸就8個月<br />\n一鳩樣"},{"pid":"02a794317c8fed4e43ed64d190f32b2ee27a4056","tid":2514382,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"其實laser pointer係攻擊性武器隨左香港有冇案例<br />\n冇既話即係港共紅官9up, 咪撚再扮有普通法"},{"pid":"bfcd7c19b67cc58310499140384b1614d988fad3","tid":2514382,"uid":1988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a794317c8fed4e43ed64d190f32b2ee27a4056","tid":2514382,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"其實laser pointer係攻擊性武器隨左香港有冇案例<br />\n冇既話即係港共紅官9up, 咪撚再扮有普通法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:01:05.000Z","msg":"高院案例<br />\n件嘢只需要證明到有能力傷害到人<br />\n控方唔需要證明佢點樣用嚟攻擊人<br />\n<br />\n佢只要搵個專家證人 證明支laser pen 可以引起人眼睛傷害<br />\n哪怕個situation 喺現實到無可能發生<br />\n支laser pen 都係攻擊性武器<br />\n<br />\n嚴格嚟講<br />\n一個冇手嘅人條頸掛住把菜刀 已經足以犯 持有攻擊性武器<br />\n佢有無能力或者佢點樣可以用把菜刀傷人並不能構成爭議點"},{"pid":"2213598f31fa0e56c97b4e406e598c8b95819021","tid":2514382,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"02a794317c8fed4e43ed64d190f32b2ee27a4056","tid":2514382,"uid":65790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T10:55:04.000Z","msg":"其實laser pointer係攻擊性武器隨左香港有冇案例<br />\n冇既話即係港共紅官9up, 咪撚再扮有普通法"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:07:11.000Z","msg":"呢個就係普通法的特色黎<br />\n法官本身就係一個立法者<br />\n藏有攻擊性武器係犯法<br />\n但係咩係攻擊性武器就有好大自由度任由個法官詮釋 <br />\n本來呢種自由度係比法官喺判案的時候更加符合社會的現實環境<br />\n但呢種自由度喺港共手上就變成任意判決的武器"},{"pid":"e762c412392db87d8b882c3b09dd2e27848230cd","tid":2514382,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f595249459cece22501fb4cc1dcee313d3eaa16","tid":2514382,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"法庭接納被告將涉案物品帶入理大時沒有傷人意圖，但離開理大時有關意圖已改變<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"意圖要睇被捕當日"},{"pid":"76b9f9c9b8d78b1ce7ae153b22c07f9d8e3e7b1b","tid":2514382,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e762c412392db87d8b882c3b09dd2e27848230cd","tid":2514382,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f595249459cece22501fb4cc1dcee313d3eaa16","tid":2514382,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"法庭接納被告將涉案物品帶入理大時沒有傷人意圖，但離開理大時有關意圖已改變<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:08:13.000Z","msg":"意圖要睇被捕當日"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T11:09:10.000Z","msg":"意圖係睇港共心情"},{"pid":"e2096f196ed257f460abe3b75d8ed11200483978","tid":2514382,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"76b9f9c9b8d78b1ce7ae153b22c07f9d8e3e7b1b","tid":2514382,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e762c412392db87d8b882c3b09dd2e27848230cd","tid":2514382,"uid":87985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8f595249459cece22501fb4cc1dcee313d3eaa16","tid":2514382,"uid":182197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T09:14:38.000Z","msg":"法庭接納被告將涉案物品帶入理大時沒有傷人意圖，但離開理大時有關意圖已改變<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/asset